WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.500
Welcome to the Cognee Release Root-Cause Analysis (RCA) dashboard playground.

00:04.500 --> 00:08.500
Viewing the Quickstart Documentation tab for setting up Cognee on your own project.

00:08.500 --> 00:11.000
Returning to the Playground Console where the Code Knowledge Graph is currently empty.

00:11.000 --> 00:16.500
Clicking Ingest Demo Repo. Tree-Sitter AST parsing and Git release sync construct the graph.

00:16.500 --> 00:25.500
Graph construction completes with 39 edges. INC-1001 (Python Checkout failures) is selected.

00:25.500 --> 00:29.000
Clicking Run Graph RCA to start traversing the call-graph calls and imports.

00:29.000 --> 00:32.500
Traversing complete. Surfacing app.payments.process_payment as the root-cause candidate.

00:32.500 --> 00:43.500
Clicking View Diff. Git diff pane slides open showing code modifications in payments.py.

00:43.500 --> 00:46.500
Selecting INC-1002 (Python receipt display shows N/A) in the incident list.

00:46.500 --> 00:50.000
Clicking Run Graph RCA to traverse the call-graph from the receipt traceback frames.

00:50.000 --> 00:53.000
Traversing completes, identifying app.utils.format_currency as the root-cause candidate.

00:53.000 --> 00:59.000
Clicking View Diff to inspect the exact format code modifications inside app/utils.py.

00:59.000 --> 01:02.000
Selecting INC-1004 (Chronological R1 validation error) in the incident list.

01:02.000 --> 01:05.500
Clicking Run Graph RCA to trace the card validation error back through the graph.

01:05.500 --> 01:08.500
Traversing completes, surfacing app.payments.validate_card as the root-cause culprit.

01:08.500 --> 01:13.000
Clicking View Diff to review card validation modifications in app/payments.py.
